            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Maximus <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>Antonior</abbr><ex>um</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>lib</abbr><ex>ertus</ex></expan> et <lb n="3"/>Vercilla <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>ivi</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ecerunt</ex></expan> sibi et <lb n="4"/>Nundinae <expan><abbr>fil</abbr><ex>iae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>norum</ex></expan> V <lb n="5"/>et Urso filio <expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>norum</ex></expan> XXX
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Oberhalb des Inschriftfeldes Lorbeerkranz in einem Halbreis, links und rechts darüber Delphine. Möglicherweise ehemals Teil eines Grabbaus.</p>
            </div>
